1 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
2 commend the American Shore and Beach Preservation Association on the occasion of its one
3 hundredth anniversary; does hereby recognize ASBPA's collaborative efforts to advocate for
4 the betterment and preservation of the American coast for current and future generations;
5 does hereby extend enduring appreciation for its continued preparation for the future
6 challenges of coastal science and policy; and does hereby commend ASBPA's founding
7 purpose to promote the health and physical well-being of all Americans through the careful
8 stewardship of the United States' coasts and shores.
